{"word":"Scepter","slug":"scepter","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Scepter</b> A wand used by kings to signify favor or disfavor to those who desired audience<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=5&verse=2'>Est 5:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=8&verse=4'>Est 8:4</a><br/> A symbol of authority<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=24&verse=17'>Num 24:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=14&verse=5'>Isa 14:5</a><br/> Made of gold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=4&verse=11'>Est 4:11</a><br/> Made of iron<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=2&verse=9'>Psa 2:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=2&verse=27'>Rev 2:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=12&verse=5'>Rev 12:5</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=10'>Gen 49:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=24&verse=17'>Num 24:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=9&verse=4'>Isa 9:4</a>"}]}